This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with acoustic models and language processing. The use of deep Transformer networks also suggests a focus on natural language processing. 

It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with acoustic models and audio processing. 

cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely sub-category as the paper proposes a new architecture for deep learning models. 

cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possibility as the paper mentions results on a large scale video dataset, suggesting a focus on visual data. 

Finally, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper deals with deep learning models and their performance improvements.
